sentences.sentence: Selected from the world-renowned Qingyuan shiitake mushroom with a high degree of effective active ingredients.
sentences.translation: 选自世界知名的庆元香菇，有效成分极高的香菇。

sentences.sentence: He measured antioxidant capacity in several kinds of mushrooms. They included the common white button mushroom, shiitake mushrooms, and oyster mushrooms.
sentences.translation: 他测量了数种菇类中的抗氧化能力。他们涵盖了一般的洋菇、茸及蠔菇。

sentences.sentence: Natural Shiitake Complex has been shown to work similarly to an enzyme found naturally in the skin to accelerate cell turnover and renewal for healthy, younger-looking skin.
sentences.translation: 天然的喷鼻菇萃取物经表明有雷同酵素的效用，可以加快皮肤的新陈代谢，获得更为健康年青的皮肤表面。
